},{"pid":"e48c96229db01c65a04428bf7b7f2a2c9f05e964","tid":418541,"uid":55048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T03:19:56.000Z","msg":"爆爆爆 個個月都話爆 爆條鐵咩 石就有得爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ddef00ab7d1be1c8adb012d2c40983b7cf15a67","tid":418541,"uid":20805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T03:32:44.000Z","msg":"太睇少香港有錢個班了<br />\n隨時拿錢掃貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上星期先買完比個女， 今個星期就問，有冇咩野好買<br />\n利申:做地產"},{"pid":"c068e4994872692556732e3ee31b6bcd437d0b9e","tid":418541,"uid":142475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T03:48:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>銀行都唔借其實已經係個泡沫警號黎<br />\n發展商仲幫手推高個價</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n銀行不知幾樂意借,係金管局唔俾佢地借咁多"},{"pid":"c1d1bc17157094c748925cf27f1d26de61c507f0","tid":418541,"uid":25900,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T03:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港樓市爆<br />\n等於全球金融危機<br />\n<br />\n中美俄歐都唔會畀佢發生<br />\n<br />\n有能力就梗係買<br />\n<br />\n唔買過幾年上車盤變六百萬三百呎真係喊都無謂<br />\n<br />\n講真就算跌最多只會高位回一成半至兩成</blockquote><br />\n中美俄歐都唔會畀佢發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾弱智先講得出"},{"pid":"76f04321f21fe69bf0059fea6af75434487b7aae","tid":418541,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T03:57:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>傻撚左個鼻<br />\n跌一成都有大把人接貨</blockquote><br />\n跌夠兩成有冇人敢接<br />\n同股市一樣根本<br />\n值唔值唔係睇高位落左幾多<br />\n睇將來</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯,好多人睇好,又話現價嫌貴/細/遠, 跌果刻又冇勇氣接, 失敗者就喜歡俾藉口自己證實乜都唔做先係合理。的確衝出comfort zone要冒險同辛苦,但永遠留在comfort zone, 只會慢慢被社會淘汰"},{"pid":"9143c0015e3875bf2e87fd22a96e20a6cf1faf86","tid":418541,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"無人理縮表"},{"pid":"16c20e988ba5fe19325b3838bd7d980678a258aa","tid":418541,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T04:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太睇少香港有錢個班了<br />\n隨時拿錢掃貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上星期先買完比個女， 今個星期就問，有冇咩野好買<br />\n利申:做地產</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港好多隱形富豪,睇下周街咁多舖位單位邊個收緊租? 最慘係果班明明係窮人,但以為自己係中產,可以過中產生活既人。"},{"pid":"f10a027d5f36f99ca054c98a92fa262bedecc78b","tid":418541,"uid":39846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T04:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>港版次按直頭同美國次按風暴一模一樣<br />\n見到咁多傻仔無視風險入市, 真係好似股市牛3一樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁先正<br />\n<br />\n唔大爆破, 我邊有機會買平野呢？<br />\n<br />\n黎多一次2003年大平賣<br />\n<br />\n我真係去買兩間地舖, 養六代<br />\n<br />\n賺到D租金用黎資助義士</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你嘅假定要建基於香港真係有&ldquo;將來&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得世道同零三，零八已經好唔同。<br />\n零三年香港仲未咁單一化。世界仲係叫香港做香港。今日係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，心照不宣啦。"},{"pid":"c25509d7979292e1277095643bee0b54421d5564","tid":418541,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774c7cfd1a433ceca8f4eb08279c0fb0810ae168","tid":418541,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>港版次按直頭同美國次按風暴一模一樣<br />\n見到咁多傻仔無視風險入市, 真係好似股市牛3一樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁先正<br />\n<br />\n唔大爆破, 我邊有機會買平野呢？<br />\n<br />\n黎多一次2003年大平賣<br />\n<br />\n我真係去買兩間地舖, 養六代<br />\n<br />\n賺到D租金用黎資助義士</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你嘅假定要建基於香港真係有&ldquo;將來&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得世道同零三，零八已經好唔同。<br />\n零三年香港仲未咁單一化。世界仲係叫香港做香港。今日係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，心照不宣啦。</blockquote><br />\n難怪深圳樓價咁貴 原來幻想埋香港未落"},{"pid":"a9f6c5f7108e503113d15261dbda91fcf310ee54","tid":418541,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑天鵝<br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n灰犀牛"},{"pid":"96e29dce4f93e88954cc762d2c1b4c4633046367","tid":418541,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f91e99d52ff735d2775c1169b1e2fb48d01a7d0","tid":418541,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:46:25.000Z","msg":"好呀 跌多d"},{"pid":"25147595d83836df8c1f602dc32dd699b315701d","tid":418541,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:07:18.000Z","msg":"好奇一問，係咪即係類似NINJA LOAN?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c55a6fbd3a4bed42dca2c019737d92d6fbba84","tid":418541,"uid":69013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:15:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1997年4月香港銀行總存款: 2.6萬億港元<br />\n2017年2月香港銀行總存款: 11.9萬億港元<br />\n<br />\n點睇以上數據，仲有一班大業主已經供完，日日收租<br />\n<br />\n我都好想爆，但感覺上需要加息五里以上先會有影響</blockquote><br />\n黑天鵝<br />\n97經濟咁好都可以爆<br />\n冇野冇可能<br />\n睇你有沒有耐性</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n97爆唔係得香港爆<br />\n當時結合左主權易交，東南亞地區經濟過度膨脹被索羅斯為首既基金追擊，俄羅斯經濟問題先爆到 <br />\n<br />\n淨香港因素好難爆，而家個經濟基礎好穩，要爆一定係受外圍手/環球/中國因素影響，而家稍預見到係北韓危機，美國縮表。"},{"pid":"74be1716cefd3d453f70a8d81691abc7688c5e70","tid":418541,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f7e7b0266f9f1149a8d7f3abf8cbcaff1d9cc5","tid":418541,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>港版次按直頭同美國次按風暴一模一樣<br />\n見到咁多傻仔無視風險入市, 真係好似股市牛3一樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁先正<br />\n<br />\n唔大爆破, 我邊有機會買平野呢？<br />\n<br />\n黎多一次2003年大平賣<br />\n<br />\n我真係去買兩間地舖, 養六代<br />\n<br />\n賺到D租金用黎資助義士</blockquote><br />\n巴打一定full pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8804c5b5b4e6aaaa56a5a346d534ef98b8d44b13","tid":418541,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1b19c22cf54bccbd791211b8b0ac73cce8913b","tid":418541,"uid":25971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T08:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太睇少香港有錢個班了<br />\n隨時拿錢掃貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上星期先買完比個女， 今個星期就問，有冇咩野好買<br />\n利申:做地產</blockquote><br />\n樓價過兩年升一倍不是夢"},{"pid":"9fe39976a803716ab9c1400bb4aa81f2faedd4a4","tid":418541,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"係，好似等支爆咁<br />\n<br />\n唔等支爆一早識買樓果班人已經上晒岸啦<br />\n<br />\n只係幾年既事"},{"pid":"b95ed8a7d2ba5b088d27b00fde30a775debb75bb","tid":418541,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea56e8082ab24ba7b87a8d94934bf4ac27e675d","tid":418541,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:55:19.000Z","msg":"睇唔到會跌，無錢等訓街"},{"pid":"c3bf225b768aa702755ec872037a0442e9b96393","tid":418541,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:52:28.000Z","msg":"投資幾球落一個冇將來既地方，只可以祝你好運，諗清楚呢度10年後係香港定廣東省香港巿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bdf09161f6ee304d55a637c0d659c7a61e7323","tid":418541