","msg":"爆得未? 我手上幾個單位仲升緊既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce12412f953eb25aa2e579127fc3e7ae19a7a6ef","tid":418541,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc1de392e9e52c25c2fb8d9075a35ed25d0917f","tid":418541,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d87fb2195b24624a90f769b3ffb0bc64d8d514","tid":418541,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>投資幾球落一個冇將來既地方，只可以祝你好運，諗清楚呢度10年後係香港定廣東省香港巿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港市都冇阻樓價升幅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當變成香港巿時, 所謂巿價係咪真係有人接貨?"},{"pid":"d4cd05f54431ad966162a9f251b98ef0e39ded95","tid":418541,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004f38869d91382bfb40dee3f502ecf5cb665ddf","tid":418541,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ad50286b0c14006b551d5e5bfcb8935338bb50","tid":418541,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T17:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132cf1f37087726f6b4a26d62c6beacec0249e35","tid":418541,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投資幾球落一個冇將來既地方，只可以祝你好運，諗清楚呢度10年後係香港定廣東省香港巿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，你地咪年年都咁講無將來，等支爆，然後年年唔買樓，而家升到你都追唔到，就繼續用無前途去掩飾買唔到樓既哥悲<br />\n<br />\n其實你一早肯買，已經賺左將球，咁你就唔會覺得無前途<br />\n<br />\n等支爆果班睇錯市中晒招，市場會罰睇錯市既人，你地的確係無前途"},{"pid":"e61303f67c953038fcd1fd210483a8010b71cfde","tid":418541,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T04:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07afc67b4f0544535ae39d493c3a97a904276f3","tid":418541,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T04:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個個月都話爆<br />\n個個月都升<br />\n究竟幾時爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會爆 快些買樓</blockquote><br />\n買到一早買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都想佢爆之後入市</blockquote><br />\n所以個市係點都唔會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}